  "remarks": "GBi.007 Designation: a) Lieutenant-colonel b) Head of the Armed Forces Military Hospital. Passport no: SA0002264, issued on 24 Jul. 2006, issued in Guinea-Bissau (Expiration date 23 Jul. 2009). Other information: Na Man was listed on 18 Jul. 2012 pursuant to paragraph 4 of resolution 2048 (2012) as “Member of the “Military Command” which has assumed responsibility for the coup d'état of 12 April 2012. Also a member of the Military High Command (highest hierarchy of the Bissau-Guinean Armed Forces).” Father’s name is Biute Naman; Mother’s name is Ndjade Na Noa.; Listing: Listed by 2048 Committee on 18 Jul. 2012",
